    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>The blade of this glaive is serrated and mounted on an axle, around which a heavy cord is wrapped.</em></p>\n<p>When the cord is pulled as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Move-Actions\">move action</a>, the blade spins rapidly for a number of rounds equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Strength</a>&nbsp;bonus. While the blade is spinning, you gain a +2 bonus on damage rolls with the weapon. When the blade is not spinning, treat this weapon as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/weapon-descriptions/glaive\">glaive</a>.</p>",
